50:["$","div",null,{"className":"my-4 flex gap-3 rounded-xl border-l-4 p-4 shadow-sm bg-yellow-50 border-yellow-300","children":[["$","div",null,{"className":"mt-0.5 shrink-0","children":"$15:props:children:0:props:children"}],["$","div",null,{"className":"prose-sm","children":["$","p",null,{"children":[["$","strong",null,{"children":"Fallback 安全考慮："}]," 唔好將 Fallback 設為能力太弱或安全性低嘅模型。弱模型更容易被 prompt injection 攻擊——尤其係 Crawler Agent 會接觸不受信任嘅網頁內容。詳細睇",["$","a",null,{"href":"/security/essential-guide","children":"安全避坑指南"}],"。"]}]}]]}]
