53:["$","h2",null,{"className":"mt-12 mb-4 border-l-4 border-red-600 pl-4 text-2xl font-bold","id":"faq","children":["$","a",null,{"href":"#faq","children":"FAQ"}]}]
54:["$","p",null,{"children":["$","strong",null,{"children":"Q：一定要畀錢先用到 OpenClaw？"}]}]
55:["$","p",null,{"children":"唔使。有兩個免費方法：一係用 OpenAI Codex OAuth（有免費額度，唔使信用卡）；二係跑 Ollama 本地模型（完全免費，但需要 Apple Silicon 或 GPU）。OpenClaw 軟件本身係開源免費，費用只嚟自 LLM API 使用量。"}]
56:["$","p",null,{"children":["$","strong",null,{"children":"Q：API Key 存喺邊？安唔安全？"}]}]
57:["$","p",null,{"children":["API Key 存喺你本機嘅 ",["$","code",null,{"className":"rounded bg-red-50 px-1.5 py-0.5 text-sm font-mono text-red-700","children":"~/.openclaw/"}]," 目錄入面（加密儲存）。喺正常情況下係安全嘅。主要風險係惡意 Skills——如果你裝咗惡意嘅社區 Skill，佢有機會讀取你嘅本地檔案，包括 API Key。所以裝 Skill 之前一定要做安全審查，詳細睇",["$","a",null,{"href":"/security/essential-guide","children":"安全避坑指南"}],"。"]}]
58:["$","p",null,{"children":["$","strong",null,{"children":"Q：可唔可以同時設定幾個 Provider？"}]}]
59:["$","p",null,{"children":["可以。你可以為唔同 Agent 設唔同嘅 Provider 同模型，例如 Main Agent 用 Claude Sonnet、Crawler Agent 用 DeepSeek、Coder Agent 用 GPT-5.4。用 ",["$","code",null,{"className":"rounded bg-red-50 px-1.5 py-0.5 text-sm font-mono text-red-700","children":"openclaw config set agents.<agent-name>.model <model-id>"}]," 逐個設定。"]}]
5a:["$","p",null,{"children":["$","strong",null,{"children":"Q：點知我用咗幾多錢？"}]}]
5b:["$","p",null,{"children":["兩個地方睇：TUI 底部嘅實時 token 顯示（",["$","code",null,{"className":"rounded bg-red-50 px-1.5 py-0.5 text-sm font-mono text-red-700","children":"tokens X/Y (Z%)"}],"）可以見到當前 session 消耗；去各 Provider 嘅 dashboard（OpenAI Usage、Anthropic Console、DeepSeek Dashboard）可以睇到實際費用同歷史用量。建議每個 Provider 都設用量上限，詳細方法睇",["$","a",null,{"href":"/troubleshoot/token-optimization","children":"Token 慳錢攻略"}],"。"]}]
5c:["$","p",null,{"children":["$","strong",null,{"children":"Q：OpenRouter 同直接用各 Provider 有乜實際分別？"}]}]
5d:["$","p",null,{"children":"功能上一樣，主要分別係：直連 Provider 冇加成、latency 低、Provider 直接支持；OpenRouter 方便統一管理、一個 dashboard 睇晒所有用量，但每次呼叫有少量加成（通常 0–5%），多一層中間商。如果你只用一兩個 Provider，直連更好；如果你經常換模型做測試，OpenRouter 更方便。"}]
